logical samples revealed no evidence of CoV infection among the enrolled individuals. We identified higher levels of exposure to bats in people working in crop production and in hunting, trapping and fishing. Finally, we used the 'Spillover' risk-ranking tool to assess the potential for viral spillover and concluded that, while there is no evidence to suggest imminent risk of spillover for these CoVs, their host range and other traits suggest caution and vigilance are warranted in people with high exposure risk.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Lange, Christian E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Coulibaly, Julien Kalpy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ako, Aristide Beranger Ako", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "N'dri Vakou, Sabine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Koffi, Eug\u00e8ne Kouassi", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mendelsohn, Emma", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ball, Shannon", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Martinez, Stephanie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Francisco, Leilani", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Saylors, Karen", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Manzan, Jean", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bamba, Djeneba", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kouakou, Val\u00e8re", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Koui, Stephane Tossea", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Frantz, Jean-Louis", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Joly, Damien", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yapi, Cyprien", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Daszak, Peter", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dosso, Mireille", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Laudisoit, Anne", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/6c0f20e4047be843ba6701708a434d10", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/f460af58bb450d8ab60a92bf29b6a8ee7ac2162db6e26f6fff1a63062aeaa5aa", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero:/